    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Brigitte stays glued to her frontline, using Shield Bash to stop a diver mid-engage and Repair Pack to keep her tank topped off during extended trades.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her healing output is low compared to dedicated healers and she has almost no range, so she contributes little if her team isn't actively brawling at close quarters.</p>"
